{"tid":2210561,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"網民在青衣城發起「和你Dinner」行動","createTime":"2020-09-20T13:23:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T18:33:27.000Z","uid":79563,"like":537,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":132,"replies":[{"pid":"21b02895d9603d2fd117646f79af225bb7e72e2c","tid":2210561,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T13:23:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1550672-20200920.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1550672-20200920.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=eCiXx0TsV7ZnsYjNRM2Ommo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=19838325\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1550672-20200920.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=eb8e76f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1550672-20200920.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n有網民發起青衣城「和你Dinner」行動。晚上7時，數十名市民在商場內高叫口號及唱反修例歌曲，又舉起「五一」手勢。<br />\n<br />\n有市民穿上寫有「人人都係快必」的黃色上衣，聲援被控發表煽動文字等罪名的人民力量副主席譚得志。<br />\n<br />\n一批軍裝警員其後到場拉起封鎖線，截查在場人士，並要求在場圍觀的市民離開，指他們有機會違反限聚令。"},{"pid":"0ce6ab0043c84084381515c6b84592885cd0e100","tid":2210561,"uid":177089,"like":5,"dislike":14,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T13:23:26.000Z","msg":"和你癲"},{"pid":"ec1bc896a1b8e8d4074e0d771437e4c582bb78be","tid":2210561,"uid":199893,"like":64,"dislike":6,"score":58,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T13:24:04.000Z","msg":"班狗驚了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58732bb3526ae630733d07f54f7b30dabfbcd77e","tid":2210561,"uid":284432,"like":241,"dislike":9,"score":232,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T13:24:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0f5f4f4348802dac74b32d294dbc3e7f621eb88e","tid":2210561,"uid":264529,"like":79,"dislike":5,"score":74,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T13:25:08.000Z","msg":"十幾個人引左百幾驚力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99bec126d2afbb257af2e9